links.label: Are you affected? Take the survey.

config.text: Description: additional information about this infographic.

about.aboutContent:
The purpose of the 1000words application is to showcase the collective dissemination of user input reports on various flood conditions as they progress, as well as to showcase how real time water level statistics and user inputs would be shown directly from provincial gauges and the dedicated citizen observatory survey, linked to the map itself.

Please fill the Citizen Observation input:
Drive Through : Are vehicles at a normal size able to pass?
Walk Through: Are pedestrian able to pass?
Water Level Rank: Please estimate a number from 0 to 10 to indicate how high is the water level in reference to the nearest curb. 
0 - Street Level
5 - Halfway up the curb
10 - Curb is fully covered
Attachments: Please attach if available photos of the spot

Find the survey here.
